Privacy Policy

Last updated: 6/29/2023

This Privacy Policy describes how Evelynn Discord bot ("us", "we", or "our") collects, uses, and shares personal information and other data from users ("you" or "users") in connection with the use of the Evelynn Discord bot.

By using Evelynn Discord bot, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect
Evelynn Discord bot collects the following information:

Server Information: We may collect certain server-related information, such as server names and IDs, to provide and improve our services.
Data Usage
Evelynn Discord bot uses the collected information for the following purposes:

To provide and maintain the services of Evelynn Discord bot.
To personalize and improve the user experience.
To analyze and monitor the usage of Evelynn Discord bot.
To communicate with users and respond to their inquiries.
To enforce our Terms of Service and other applicable policies.
Data Security
We prioritize the security of your data and have implemented appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect it. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

Sharing of Information
We do not share personal information with third parties unless required for legal reasons or to provide and improve our services.

Compliance with Laws and Legal Requests
We may disclose your personal information in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to:

Comply with a legal obligation.
Protect and defend the rights or property of Evelynn Discord bot.
Prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing in connection with Evelynn Discord bot.
Protect the personal safety of users or the public.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. We advise you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Your Acceptance of These Terms
By using Evelynn Discord bot, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to this policy, please refrain from using Evelynn Discord bot.

Contacting Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at 010000001011e@protonmail.com.
